{"tid":1823097,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[黃藍大戰] 燒山對哈佛大學博士師弟，又勝一仗","createTime":"2020-01-13T11:44:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T02:41:31.000Z","uid":88743,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9377ac8ca28804ee53876c3b517ceeb5cdf33018","tid":1823097,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T11:44:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Vj8IZ_kCxwg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVj8IZ_kCxwg&d=x7%2Fg1uS4a%2BT3911x%2BwLoHFHO27hz5fVRhbnvZL2FK%2Bg%3D&h=87e70540\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Vj8IZ_kCxwg</a><br />\n<br />\n吳錦宇(Michael Ng-Quinn)是我聖保羅書院的學弟，他1969年赴美升學，畢業於芝加哥大學，後獲哈佛大學博士。曾任教於塔夫茲大學(Tufts University)的佛萊契爾法律與外交學院( Fletcher School of Law and Diplomacy)以及其他大學，研究領域主要是國際關係、美國外交政策，比較外交政策(亞洲為主)，以及比較政治(中國為主)。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 普世價值的問題。<br />\n<br />\n2. 如一個國家的政治制度是一黨專政，而又沒有alternative system 的話，那麼反對執政黨是否等於反對這個國家？換句話說，就是要革命了。對嗎？<br />\n<br />\n3. 五大訴求是否可以實現的？如不是，那麼這個運動的目的是甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n4. 香港真的不夠自由嗎？"},{"pid":"8c034fa4338e3521915cf279e3afbf069a57fee3","tid":1823097,"uid":221265,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T13:26:31.000Z","msg":"嗰條阿伯極恐怖"},{"pid":"468e59057ed53fc0d1c1461017737abe0663c68d","tid":1823097,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8c034fa4338e3521915cf279e3afbf069a57fee3","tid":1823097,"uid":221265,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T13:26:31.000Z","msg":"嗰條阿伯極恐怖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T02:27:06.000Z","msg":"好彩有蕭生<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6574754b5a5bd265d79f3f4d2c0442b4bea03bcf","tid":1823097,"uid":24284,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T02:36:25.000Z","msg":"唔講唔知佢讀哈佛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n順片幫佢做中國人，取消美國護照/綠卡"},{"pid":"bd16ae3b156ca473ddeb2495152e2525b987d2ab","tid":1823097,"uid":228143,"like":0,"disl